Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是「泥華留斗」的總長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是狂犬 狂犬澤村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小弟好像受了你們不少招待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份禮我得要好好回應才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我這惡魔的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真不愧是澤村老大 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要找我來幫忙的話 就挑些更厲害的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有欺負弱小的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請跟我交往好嗎 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三振出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束 哈里斯塔夫第二十一 連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這第二十一次連敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘍唆 才第二十次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周同一時間請繼續收看遊星少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 澤村正治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在沒有女友的情況下渡過了十七年又兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續二十次失戀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今紀錄持續刷新中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一份大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 你們少在我面前卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每個人都是這副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了別叫我大哥哥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到馬子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管 走開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來當你的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管不著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真空虛 太空虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想交個平凡的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與她共度平凡甜蜜的校園生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打架再怎麼強也沒任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人都怕我 就連女生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是高中三年都交不到女友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把右手當女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣灰暗的青春真是太悲慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們一直做個朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都好 來當我的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 剛剛的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會幻聽 看來這次傷的可真嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又 又聽到女孩子的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音更清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭 頭好暈… 牧繪小姐 快拿藥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 冷靜下來正治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是什麼玩意啊！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天 右手的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的 你是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的袖口會有女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是正治 這不是作夢 真的是正治耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為什麼我會在正治的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問你 為什麼右手會有胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 會有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 為什麼你會認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我… 一直都在暗戀著你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗… 暗戀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從三年前第一眼看見就喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在想如果能跟正治在一起該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是我有生以來第一次被人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這一點也不值得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被右手告白一點也不值得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是暗戀還是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白點這樣讓我很困擾 我手變這樣你叫我怎麼生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話 話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是醒了過來就在你的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:09:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道原因 其實我也是害怕到想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能夠在心愛的正治身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也有些開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿個頭 我可是一點都不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被稱為「狂犬澤村」令人畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 我宰了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是不倫不類了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力讓別人害怕助你一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這傢伙的實體又怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜誌還是收在同一個地方比較好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的報紙跟雜誌也都成為文明垃圾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為有些凌亂 所以我想整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好像也不壞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小… 小奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床底下也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都丟掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要任意決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你家在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去你家的話就有可能知道你為什會變成這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不想變回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這樣不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大 昨天真是多謝啦… 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是忙著打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧他不在 今天終於能夠清靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 班長 跟我來辦公室拿參考資料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 傲慢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瑪琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鳥 美鳥！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 這是你家？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好大!! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個千金大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我看還是回去吧 我覺得這樣子也沒什麼不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是貴府小姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐有事外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天可能回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大會是感冒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探病看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宮原同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴨蔥女高的小姐們找我有何貴事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們是澤村的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你就在這裡 卻說另一個你外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 這下真的糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為能跟最喜歡的正治在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是在月台上看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一直都只是在很遠的地方看著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小倉橋高中的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是大小姐 還是個優等生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們都聽說正治是櫻田門高中的不良而感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道 其實是個很溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在幫助弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡那樣的正治了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 現在我非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 昨天真是太感謝了 今天是怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只是有點小感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去探望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大 現在我們就過去探望你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼大不了的 我沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我現在可是跟崇拜你的女孩子在一起噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人說要過去探望你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎麼喜歡我 我還是不會喜歡上變成右手的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我覺得很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴望的是人類的女友而不是右手的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不要出聲 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 宮原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要猛按門鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是優子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是由香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆嘵 全中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 我是澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮原那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去便利商店買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母在國外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有個姊姊 不過一直待在男友那很少回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次我們做飯給你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請品嚐我們做的 滿懷愛意的高麗菜肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆嘵 滿懷愛的高麗菜肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 洗手間在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 走廊左邊轉角就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮原那傢伙怎麼這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喜歡年紀比自己還小的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為您現在好像沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果我可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆嘵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了 沉寂了十七年又兩個月 我的春天終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀比我小的 我也交往了二十個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以吻你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 怎麼這麼大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞 請閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是「泥華留斗」的女成員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是來替被你打進醫院的男友報仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 你有沒有在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來 澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢… 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 就用這個一刀解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請饒過我們一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治才是 沒事吧 有沒有受傷？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 剛才我暈了過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我守住約定了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有發出聲音噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直都在暗戀著正治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鳥 我叫春日野美鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 美鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後 像這時候就別管什麼約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出個聲通知我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果我的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 那到時候再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓女孩子受傷 這樣的守密也沒任何意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然變成了我的右手 但你好歹也是個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡正治了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村老大 你不要緊吧 剛剛那些女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 放手 離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像這樣跟最喜歡的正治在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在依然就像是在作夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是作為女友而只是右手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人有些遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果這秘密在這世上只有我們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想的話 我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次在正治的房裡看到的月亮非常的漂亮
